<p
  style="color:#4b5563;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 16px 0;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;"
>{{#if firstName}}Hola {{firstName}},{{else}}Hola,{{/if}}</p>
<h2
  style="color:#1a1a1a;margin:0 0 8px 0;font-size:20px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;"
>Solicitud de restablecimiento de contrasena</h2>
<p
  style="color:#4b5563;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 24px 0;font-size:16px;font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Arial,sans-serif;"
